-- HCL Technologies, Ingram Micro May Buy Sonata Stake, Economic Times Says
-- B y   A d i   N a r a y a n
-- 2010-11-02T02:17:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/hcl-technologies-ingram-micro-may-buy-sonata-stake-economic-times-says.html
HCL Technologies Ltd. and Ingram
Micro Inc. are considering buying stakes in India’s Sonata
Software Ltd., Economic Times reported, citing three people it
didn’t identify.  An unidentified spokesperson for HCL said they “do not
comment on market speculation,” the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adi Narayan in Mumbai at 
